    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "tools_list",
      "x": 670,
      "y": 60,
      "width": 380,
      "height": 300,
      "text": "1. HighLevel CRM    → Update leads, tasks, pipeline stages\n2. Google Calendar   → Schedule calls, showings, open houses\n3. Gmail             → Emails, brochures, CC/BCC\n4. Slack             → Team notifications, approvals\n5. Google Sheets     → Log leads, errors, analytics\n6. DocuSign          → E-signature documents\n7. Twilio            → SMS notifications, reminders\n8. Notion            → Knowledge base, SOPs\n9. Zapier            → External automations\n10. Compliance Agent  → Regulatory review (sub-agent)",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "originalText": "1. HighLevel CRM    → Update leads, tasks, pipeline stages\n2. Google Calendar   → Schedule calls, showings, open houses\n3. Gmail             → Emails, brochures, CC/BCC\n4. Slack             → Team notifications, approvals\n3. Google Sheets     → Log leads, errors, analytics\n4. Slack             → Team notifications, approvals\n6. DocuSign          → E-signature documents\n7. Twilio            → SMS notifications, reminders\n8. Notion            → Knowledge base, SOPs\n9. Zapier            → External automations\n10. Compliance Agent  → Regulatory review (sub-agent)",
